# Clarity Engine — GPT Integration
# Copy this file to .env and add your OpenAI API key

# Get your key at https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
VITE_OPENAI_KEY=sk-...your-key-here...

# Without this key, the Clarity Engine runs in demo mode
# using local fallback logic. Everything still works,
# but the graph nodes and insights are generated locally
# instead of by GPT.
